Interface INmNode

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity, IIdentifiable, IReferrable
    All Known Subinterfaces:

    public interface INmNode
extends IEntity, IIdentifiable
    INmNode: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    The linking of NmEcus to NmClusters is realized via the NmNodes.
